channel.title: I need help, im not mentaly impared, dispite what you may say after reading
channel.description:
Hey, I used to run a server, when i had xp. It all worked great, but then I get vista, and stoped playing mopar all together, well now I am trying to get a server up and running agian, I port forwarded and everything, downloaded java etc. Except it always says I do not have java jdk 6.0, but I infact have it and its installed. I also am using Mod Thoraks perfect compiler so its not the compiler, I was wondering if I forgot to do anything, afterall it has been a while since I ran a server, or is it one of Vista's many security settings that are blocking it?
Picture proving I have Java - [IMG]http://i118.photobucket.com/albums/o120/Iced_Liquid/wdf-1.jpg[/img][br][size=1]Posted on: August 07, 2007, 07:09:34 PM[/size][hr]Ok, I hate double poster as much as the next guy, but I kinda need some help =(
